#Seoul isn’t just for city slickers. It’s great for nature buffs too!😎 Surrounded by beautiful forested mountains with tons of hiking trails, and easily accessible by public transport, Seoul is a rare city that offers both urban and outdoor adventures. 🏃‍♀️🏃‍♂️
#GoKorean #KoreanAir https://t.co/y3nedA5fY7

Have an easy task at hand? #Piece_of_cake🍰, right? Koreans take this saying one step further by saying “nu-wo-seo tteok meog-gi” when something is #easy, which means “you might as well be eating rice cakes while lying down”. Now that’s the life.
#goKorean #KoreanAir✈ https://t.co/kemahhKUso
